text: Jean-Jacques Gaultier Jean-Jacques Gaultier (born July 13, 1963 in Épinal, Vosges) is a member of the National Assembly of France. He represents the Vosges department, and is a member of the Republicans. He was the deputy for Vosges's 4th constituency from 2002 to 2012 and again from 2017 onwards. ==References== Category:1963 births Category:Living people Category:People from Épinal Category:Union for a Popular Movement politicians Category:The Republicans (France) politicians Category:Deputies of the 12th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 15th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic
